This paper deals with the analysis of MIMO wireless networks with beamforming, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of channel models, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the correction factor, which is a concept related to system analysis and control (cs.SY) and performance analysis (cs.PF).
